bourne-kevork-djansezian-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ozzy-osbourne-kevork-djansezian-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ozzy-osbourne-kevork-djansezian-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ozzy-osbourne-kevork-djansezian-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ozzy-osbourne-kevork-djansezian-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）</a>透露了他在今年晚些时候即将到来的“最终”<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑人安息日</a>表演的表现计划 - 请参阅他在下面必须说的话。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-interview-sharon-ozzy-osbourne-tony-iommi-health-birmingham-villa-park-final-show-new-material-3835523">沙龙·奥斯本（Sharon Osbourne）和托尼·艾奥姆（Tony Iommi</a></strong></li></ul><p>本月早些时候（2月5日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-final-show-birmingham-july-2025-metalla-slayer-pantera-line-up-tickets-3835042">这家传奇的金属乐队宣布了他们的最后现场表演，该表演将于7月5日在伯明翰举行</a>。乐队还宣布了星光熠熠的开幕式和特别嘉宾，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Metallica">Metallica</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Slayer">Slayer</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Pantera">Pantera</a> ，Pantera， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Lamb-Of-God">God的羔羊</a>，Mastodon， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mastodon">Mastodon</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Alice-In-Chains">Alice，Alice in Chains</a> ，Halestorm， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/halestorm">Halestorm</a> ，最近的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">Grammy</a> -Winners <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira</a>等。</p><p>尽管已经确认了奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）在黑安息日（Black Sabbath）的表现，但鉴于他的健康状况，他的参与程度受到质疑。然而，现在，传奇的主唱和黑暗王子已经开启了七月的黑人安息日在舞台上可以期望他在舞台上有多少球迷开放。</p><p>奥斯本说，在他在Siriusxm上的Ozzy Speaks节目的最新一集中，即将举行的演出即将到来的<a href="https://www.loudersound.com/news/sabbath-ozzy-reunion-set" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>演出</em></a>时说：“我不打算与Black Sabbath一起做一场演出，但我正在和他们一起做一些小零碎的东西。我正在尽我所能，感到舒适。” </p><figure id="attachment_3836013" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3836013" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3836013" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OzzyOsbourne-interview-story.jpg" alt="Ozzy Osbourne" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OzzyOsbourne-interview-story.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OzzyOsbourne-interview-story-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OzzyOsbourne-interview-story-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OzzyOsbourne-interview-story-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OzzyOsbourne-interview-story-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/OzzyOsbourne-interview-story-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3836013" class="wp-caption-text"> Ozzy Osbourne。图片来源：凯文·马祖（Kevin Mazur）/盖蒂（Getty）</figcaption></figure><p>奥斯本（Osbourne）最后一次在2018年进行了全套演出，他补充说：“我想重新站起来。当您早上起床时，您就跳下床。我必须平衡自己，但我还没有死。我仍在积极做事。”</p><p>此更新是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-says-he-cant-walk-ahead-of-black-sabbaths-final-show-sharon-says-illness-doesnt-affect-his-voice-3835987">Ozzy透露，他现在由于帕金森氏病而“无法走路”</a> 。但是，他的妻子和经理沙龙向粉丝们保证，他的病“不会影响他的声音”。帕金森氏症是一种进步疾病。这不是您可以稳定的东西。它会影响身体的不同部位，并影响了他的腿。但是他的声音和以往一样好。”她解释说。</p><p>沙龙<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-sabbath-interview-sharon-ozzy-osbourne-tony-iommi-health-birmingham-villa-park-final-show-new-material-3835523">上周在维拉公园（Villa Park）与NME一起在<em>NME</em>上发表讲话时</a>解释说，她的丈夫Ozzy目前在最后的安息日表演中表现“非常出色”，并感到“非常激动”。她说：“这就是他想要的。” “他想对所有人表示感谢。由于病的病，他没有机会，但是现在他确实有机会。”</p><p>沙龙告诉<em>NME</em> ，“回到起点”将是“庆祝仍然活着的旧音乐”，而不是黑安息日发行任何新音乐。她解释说：“您进入职业生涯的舞台，无论您做什么都不能忍受您以前所做的事情。” “能够在桂冠上休息，说：&#39;人们仍然喜欢它，它仍然在卖出，我们不能比我们所做的事情更好”，这足够了。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFu3ZyBzEea/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,6