true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">杰出首次亮相奖的获奖者是Kneecap的Rich Peppiatt <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f44f.png" alt="👏" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/KNEECAPCEOL?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@kneecapceol</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/CurzonFilm?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@curzonfilm</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/EEBAFTAs?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#eebaftas</a> <a href="https://t.co/96LVasmXmh">pic.twitter.com/96lvasmxmh</a></p><p> -  BAFTA（@BAFTA） <a href="https://twitter.com/BAFTA/status/1891208219134951799?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年2月16日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>他继续说：“<i>膝盖</i>不仅仅是一部电影。” “这是一种运动，这是关于每个人都应该如何尊重自己的语言，他们应该受到尊重的文化，应该受到尊重的家园。因此，这个奖项是致力于在战斗的每个人。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-films-2024-3817632"><i>Kneecap</i>被<i>NME</i>评为2024年最佳电影</a>，他指出：“受到三分之二的经历在贝尔法斯特（Belfast）陷入困境的经历的启发 - 以及他们的机智和无尽的想象力 - 这款黑暗喜剧comedy cum docudrama cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum cum compitiation cum compitization cum compitization cum compational cum comptipation cum pickitiational comptipational comptialized rom Story to经销商Móglaí和Mo在被共和党人和忠诚主义者殴打时，他们都会陷入困境。最终，通过毒品引起的创意弯曲者，他们发现了对与当地教师进行音乐和膝盖的热爱。从那以后，提示最有趣，最令人兴奋的乐队传记片。甚至<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher</a> ）的粉丝 - 他也讨厌一切。”</p><p>这部电影也已在今年的奥斯卡颁奖典礼上被列入了长期名单， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kneecap-respond-oscar-nominations-snub-fuck-the-oscars-free-palestine-3831509">但上个月被排除在最终提名列表之外</a>。乐队回答说：“他妈的奥斯卡。自由巴勒斯坦。”</p><p> <i>Kneecap</i> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/kneecap-film-review-biopic-michael-fassbender-3779661">在<i>NME</i>中获得了五星级评论</a>，并在Andrew Strendell写作：“毫无疑问地摇摇欲坠，勇敢， <i>Kneecap</i>并没有像它那样出色的业务 - 不仅是2024年杰出的电影之一，而且可以说是最好的音乐传记之一有史以来。因此，有了很多思考和时间渗透，这是您的完整分析：天哪，他妈的我，一部电影。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-baftas-2025-3838432">BAFTA的最大获胜者是<i>席位</i>和<i>野蛮主义者</i></a>，每个人都拿到了四个锣。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kneecap-director-dedicates-bafta-to-everyone-who-should-have-their-homeland-respected-3838475">“ Kneecap”局长将BAFTA献给所有“应该受到尊重的家园”的每个人</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
这是Baftas 2025的所有获胜者https://www.nme.com/news/film/here-are-are-ally-all-theners-from-the-baftas-2025-3838432?utm_source = rsss＆utm_medium = rsss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign来自Baftas-2025Max Pilley Sun, 16 Feb 2025 19:56:30 +0000 Film NewsNewsBAFTA https://www.nme.com/?p=3838432 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="BAFTA" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>仪式于今晚（2月16日）在伦敦的皇家音乐厅举行，由大卫·坦南特（David Tennant）主持</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-baftas-2025-3838432">这里的帖子是BAFTA 2025的所有获奖者，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="BAFTA" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/BAFTA-Awards-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>第78届<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/bafta">BAFTA</a> （英国学院电影奖）于今晚（2月16日）举行 - 查看下面的所有获奖者。</p><p>仪式由前<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/doctor-who"><i>医生</i></a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-tennant">戴维·坦南特（David David Tennant）</a>主持，第二年参加了仪式，并在南方银行中心的伦敦皇家节日厅降落。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/baftas-2025-film-awards-nominations-full-list-3829082">提名于1月15日宣布</a>，宗教惊悚<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/conclave"><i>片</i></a>总共以12个点头前进，随后是11月11日的音乐<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/emilia-perez"><i>艾米利亚·佩雷斯（EmiliaPérez）</i></a> ，史诗般的《史诗般的野蛮主义者》（Epic <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-brutalist"><i>the Brutalist）</i></a> ，九个，七个为<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/anora"><i>Anora</i></a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/dune-part-two"><i>Dune，Dune：第二部分</i></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><i>邪恶</i></a>。</p><p>最后，最大的获奖者是爱德华·伯杰（Edward Berger）的<em>会议赛</em>和布雷迪·科贝特（Brady Corbet）的《野蛮主义者》 <em>（The Brutalist</em>布罗迪，得分和摄影。 </p><figure id="attachment_3830466" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830466" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830466" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025.jpg" alt="阿德里安·布罗迪（Adrien Brody）在“野蛮主义者”中。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/The-Brutalist-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3830466" class="wp-caption-text">阿德里安·布罗迪（Adrien Brody）在“野蛮主义者”中。图片来源：通用图片</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3816014"